      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ERAMOSA (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fourth (17.74) in a Grade 5 at Northam. Has a good record here at this journey. The form out of last race has been strong. Tough to beat if on-song. TWO TRUTHS (8) jumped from out wide and was game in defeat last start when a 1.5 lengths second (17.46) behind Defender at this track. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Expected to be in this for a long way. JIMARY JANUARY (3) was out of the placings last time when sixth at Cannington (16.64) but scored three back at Northam (17.56). Is yet to taste defeat at this course and distance. Great chance to atone. LIL MISS SOPHIE (2) is a last start winner who rates one of the chances again.",
